commit 187de8e192b2e954c7048257c78a0e26ef022da2
Author: Chris Marshall <devel.chm.01@gmail.com>
Date:   Tue Dec 20 09:41:06 2011 -0500

    Added TODO to t/limits_trans_err.t
    
